summary: Now this video felt good. Felt like old times. We've got Phil being weird, Phil little insight on caterpillars who's is so much...
body: Now this video felt good. Felt like old times. We’ve got Phil being weird, Phil little insight on caterpillars who’s is so much him, just out of the box, we’ve got some serious advice in a classic Phil fashion and the long egg thing actually made me snicker. This time it didn’t seem as rushed. Short, a tiny bit, would watch more, but hey, that’s what was missing. The longing for the video to be longer and not checking if it’s gonna end soon. I’m happy with it today
